metadata.name: Mother nature
metadata.description:
This is the first in a collection of 10 photograps that have been issued as a single, unique edition.

GIF / Photo 3072*2304 Px

It`s true masterpiece of my photo art, converted to NFT - new world of digital art, to make my digital trace forever and for all mankind. It contains 8 my favourite pics made worldwide, built up in a collage and later to an NFT.

There is no better way to describe the essence of earth landscape than pure magic.
